SignatureValueTypeImpl
public interface SignatureValueType extends org.apache.xmlbeans.XmlBase64Binary
An XML SignatureValueType(@http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#). This is an atomic type that is a restriction of org.w3.x2000.x09.xmldsig.SignatureValueType.
